{"tid":1190891,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪列治加盟曼聯 簽約三年","createTime":"2019-06-07T15:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T17:49:51.000Z","uid":50385,"like":25,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"caf2d0bfeab94e872b987a51329a98ef1c75baac","tid":1190891,"uid":50385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"Manchester United sign up youngster De Laet from Stoke<br />\n&bull; Performance-related pay deal agreed for 20-year-old defender<br />\n&bull; Potters picked up player from Royal Antwerp in August 2007<br />\nThu 8 Jan 2009 06.28 EST<br />\n<br />\nStoke City have announced that the 20-year-old defender Ritchie De Laet has moved to Manchester United and signed a three-year deal. The clubs have agreed a performance-related payment package for the player, who spent the early part of the season on loan at Wrexham.<br />\nDe Laet joined Stoke from Royal Antwerp, who have a long-standing partnership with United, in August 2007 but never made a first-team appearance.<br />\nStoke have completed the signing of the midfielder Matthew Etherington from West Ham United for an undisclosed fee.<br />\nThe 27-year-old midfielder has signed has signed a 3&frac12;-year deal at the Britannia Stadium after the clubs agreed an undisclosed fee, believed to be &pound;3m. He is expected to make his debut against Liverpool on Saturday.<br />\n<br />\nThe Stoke manager, Tony Pulis, believes Etherington's experience in the top flight will be crucial in their fight to avoid relegation.<br />\n&quot;I think Matthew feels it is right to get out of London and start again,&quot; Pulis said. &quot;Perhaps we can give him the love and care he has not had for a while.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/jan/08/transfer-window-manchesterunited\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffootball%2F2009%2Fjan%2F08%2Ftransfer-window-manchesterunited&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=d486ae00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/jan/08/transfer-window-manchesterunited</a>"},{"pid":"10bf4799b3c5e7ed4bc3155798a7ebc859c44b27","tid":1190891,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e1b5b3859a236d5179fa7f79ab6dc80517b2a4","tid":1190891,"uid":164730,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"最後有英超攞<br />\n<br />\nLeicester City<br />\nPremier League: 2015&ndash;16[36]"},{"pid":"012e72cdbedb10160e49e377aeea191440ea1425","tid":1190891,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a1f655d8d49e66626edff076cff9c79ec57d96","tid":1190891,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3680b8139c2cceddcc2cb28aa77b60b1837097ae","tid":1190891,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:41:06.000Z","msg":"樓主好狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68012dca46a75dcac9e9f30bd5d3bc8d6bd92f08","tid":1190891,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe46631e4b970dc19b0146b5e2d5350a20e511e8","tid":1190891,"uid":103947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"